title: 1994 Ladies European Tour
text:
The 1994 Ladies European Tour was a series of <a href="golf">golf</a> tournaments for elite female golfers from around the world which took place in 1994. The tournaments were sanctioned by the <a href="Ladies%20European%20Tour">Ladies European Tour</a> (LET).
Tournaments.
The table below shows the 1994 schedule. The numbers in brackets after the winners' names show the number of career wins they had on the Ladies European Tour up to and including that event. This is only shown for members of the tour. 
<a href="Women%27s%20major%20golf%20championships">Major championships</a> in bold.
